    Note over Dev,Quay: Flow 1: Workbench Image Build & Deployment

    Dev->>Konflux: Push code (rhoai-2.24 branch)
    Konflux->>Konflux: Build container images<br/>(65 Tekton pipelines)
    Konflux->>Quay: Push images<br/>HTTPS/443, TLS 1.2+<br/>Registry credentials

    Note over Operator,K8sAPI: Flow 1 cont: Image Deployment to Cluster

    Operator->>K8sAPI: Apply Kustomize manifests<br/>HTTPS/6443, TLS 1.2+<br/>ServiceAccount token
    K8sAPI-->>Operator: ImageStreams + ConfigMaps created

    Note over Dashboard,CRI: Flow 1 cont: Workbench Launch

    Dashboard->>K8sAPI: User selects workbench image<br/>HTTPS/6443, TLS 1.2+<br/>User Bearer Token
    K8sAPI-->>NotebookCtrl: Notebook CR created
    NotebookCtrl->>CRI: Create workbench pod<br/>ServiceAccount
    CRI->>Quay: Pull image by digest<br/>HTTPS/443, TLS 1.2+<br/>Image pull secret
    Quay-->>CRI: Container image layers
    CRI-->>NotebookCtrl: Pod running (UID 1001)

    Note over Browser,Workbench: Flow 2: User Accessing Workbench

    Browser->>Gateway: Access workbench URL<br/>HTTPS/443, TLS 1.2+<br/>OpenShift OAuth
    Gateway->>RBAC: Forward request<br/>HTTPS/8443, TLS 1.2+<br/>Bearer Token
    RBAC->>Workbench: Proxy to container<br/>HTTP/8888, plaintext (pod-local)<br/>Auth passed through
    Workbench-->>RBAC: JupyterLab UI response
    RBAC-->>Gateway: Response
    Gateway-->>Browser: HTTPS response
